Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:43.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What seems to be the trouble, Ryuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.81,0:02:52.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.99,0:03:06.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The corner of this page from this\Nkiller notebook is cut out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:09.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Would someone still die\Nif their name was written
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:10.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,on the part that has been cut out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:11.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.33,0:03:15.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't used it in that way,\Nso I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:19.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then do Shinigami only eat apples?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:21.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:26.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But a Shinigami's organs are devolved...\Nno, evolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:28.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So there's no need for us to eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:30.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:37.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've finally been freed,\Nbut don't leave the headquarters...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:40.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Misa comes to visit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:41.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you only chat with her\Nfor a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:45.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're free to go and have a love life\Noutside of here, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:49.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We still haven't solved the Kira case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:52.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not in the mood for love.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:56.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or, are you trying to say that\NI'm a nuisance if I stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:03:58.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.07,0:04:26.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'm in no position\Nto be punishing criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.32,0:04:29.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa, punish them for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:37.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa...\NLet's make a new world Together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.57,0:05:03.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Be...\Ncareful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.44,0:05:08.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,God...\Nis watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:17.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,please hold my hand...\NIn the dark alley.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:21.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I'm alone\Nand far away...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:27.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll always...\Nfind me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.30,0:05:35.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You tell me...\Neverything you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:41.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if...\NI don't remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.48,0:05:44.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:50.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.79,0:05:58.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But what do I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:06:07.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,once I know everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:16.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:18.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The murders of criminals have\Nbegun again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:21.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There were sixteen\Njust yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:23.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They were broadcast after\NHiguchi died...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.36,0:06:25.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's thorough, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:29.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that means that Higuchi\Nwasn't necessarily Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:31.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. We're positive that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:34.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Higuchi was the one killing criminals\Nuntil we caught him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:37.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then does that mean that\Nanother Kira has appeared-?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:41.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:43.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...curse Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:46.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira appears now...\NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:49.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:52.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only Misa...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:55.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This happened as soon as\NMisa was freed, didn't it-?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:07:00.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki, are you still saying that?\NMisa is not involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:03.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened as soon as Higuchi died.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:05.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.57,0:07:12.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if there is another notebook\Nand someone is using it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:16.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll catch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:25.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Shinigami said\Nit didn't know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:30.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone could kill by writing a name\Non a clipping from the notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:35.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:39.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...whoever writes\Na name in this notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:43.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Has to write another name\Nwithin thirteen days or die...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.27,0:07:47.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light Yagami and\NMisa Amane are alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:52.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thirteen days...\NThis is the only...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:58.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki, even if we do catch the person\Nwho was writing in the notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:02.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we really convict and punish him\Nas a serial killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:06.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:10.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He wrote countless names knowing\Nthat people would die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:12.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We should kill him
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.09,0:08:14.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,if we don't want the existence\Nof the notebook to go public.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:17.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Killing him is harsh,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:20.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I bet that's what our superiors\Nwould demand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:24.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If he admits to killing with the notebook,\Nhe would receive the death penalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:25.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or at least a life sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:29.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:33.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking, Light Yagami-?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:36.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If Misa is caught, you'd also be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:40.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's it-!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:42.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a bastard-!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:49.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light Yagami is sure that\NI'll save Misa's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:52.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to save Misa in this situation
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:57.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to write Ryuzaki's real name\Nin my notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:09:00.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And if I kill Ryuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.97,0:09:07.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll definitely affect Misa's lifespan\Nand I'll die as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.19,0:09:11.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light Yagami is making everything\Ngo his way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:16.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do, Rem?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:19.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know completely that despite\Nbeing a Shinigami,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:21.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you care about Misa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.70,0:09:26.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa's life has been halved.\NThere's no way you'd abandon her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:29.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about Misa's happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:34.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing there, Ryuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.11,0:10:42.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing there, Ryuzaki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.96,0:10:57.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Ryuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:11:01.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I'm not doing anything\Nin particular, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.09,0:11:04.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of the bells...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:05.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bells-?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:07.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:11.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The bells have been really noisy\Nthroughout the day...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:16.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.23,0:11:18.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.94,0:11:21.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They've been ringing\Nall day and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:24.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help but feel curious...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.78,0:11:28.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you suppose it's a church-?\NA wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.41,0:11:30.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or, perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:31.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Ryuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:34.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say such silly things.\NLet's go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.54,0:11:37.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:41.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything I say is\Ncomplete nonsense, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:43.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,please, don't believe any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.02,0:11:54.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:57.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Most of what you say is nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:12:00.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There would be no end if\NI took you seriously all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:03.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.86,0:12:07.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:13.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But... it's true for both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:16.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:23.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever told the truth\Nat any point since you were born?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:31.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Ryuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:34.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true, I lie once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:37.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...how many people live\Ntheir entire lives
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.06,0:12:40.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,only telling the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:44.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans aren't made perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:46.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:48.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:52.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been careful not to\Ntell lies that hurt others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:54.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:00.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.22,0:13:07.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back. We're drenched.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:09.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:23.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that was awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:27.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault.\NYou were standing in that rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.36,0:13:30.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:40.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Ryuzaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.96,0:13:42.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd help you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:44.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're vigorously\Nwiping yourself off...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.13,0:13:47.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:49.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can give you a massage as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:51.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the least I can do to atone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.01,0:13:54.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.93,0:13:56.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:57.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:06.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:08.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:19.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:24.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:48.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:49.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:54.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll soon part.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.83,0:15:03.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:08.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'll come immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.89,0:15:14.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:17.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems it went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:30.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ryuzaki!\NWhat is the meaning of this-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.24,0:15:33.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you got approval\Nfrom another country
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:34.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to use the notebook\Nfor an execution-!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:35.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Watari...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:37.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:38.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:39.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's immediately
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:42.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,make arrangements to\Ntransport the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:43.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:46.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki, what's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:49.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It means that I'm going to\Ntry out the notebook for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:54.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's pointless!\NWe don't have to do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:57.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We already know that the power\Nof the notebook is real, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:15:59.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, who's going to\Nwrite the name?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:00.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you write in the notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:04.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you have to continue writing names\Nevery thirteen days--!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:07.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who's going to write\Nthe name
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.90,0:16:11.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,is someone who'll be executed\Nwithin thirteen days.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:13.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's still alive after thirteen days...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:16.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we've made a deal\Nto commute his execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:19.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't sacrifice people's lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:21.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:23.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we just clear this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:25.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the case will be solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:31.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:32.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A blackout?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:44.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Watari?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:48.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Watari-!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:54.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Data deletion-?\NWhat's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.20,0:16:57.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told Watari to erase all information...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:17:01.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,in the event that something\Nhappened to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:03.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If something happened-?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.41,0:17:05.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:06.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the Shinigami?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:08.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I don't see him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:12.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's nowhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:13.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:15.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...\NThe Shiniga...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.79,0:17:47.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.92,0:17:48.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:55.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey--! Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:58.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!\NGet a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:19:00.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- What's this?!\N- What's going on...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:04.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:06.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.45,0:19:09.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Watari, Ryuzaki, we're next--!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:23.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:26.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, Shinigami?!\NCome out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:28.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light--!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:31.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You must know something!\NCome out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:34.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's search as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:35.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.27,0:19:37.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mogi, please take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.98,0:19:38.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.63,0:20:00.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.18,0:20:03.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this-?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:04.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sand-?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:05.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on-?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.22,0:20:10.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever it is... whatever happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.77,0:20:13.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will avenge Ryuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.48,0:20:18.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Solving this case will\Nbe our gift...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:22.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,for Watari and the\Nother victims...for all people...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:25.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.45,0:20:26.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:30.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but...we're going to be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.37,0:20:33.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that what this means?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:37.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda, if you're scared of dying,\Nleave the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.34,0:20:40.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Only people who have chosen to\Nrisk their lives should be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:43.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...no. That's right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:47.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, don't talk like Ryuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.99,0:21:05.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All those in my way\Nhave disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.20,0:21:16.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the god of the new world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.19,0:21:39.11,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}This single page Forever depressing
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.73,0:21:41.44,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A fleeting tactic in the eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.48,0:21:46.24,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Without petition evil against the law\Nchain it in prison
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.28,0:21:48.78,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Poison the notebook fear the lust
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:51.53,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Delusion of being deceived\Nperpetually drooling
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:54.16,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Judgement is "crime control" they driveled
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.29,0:21:56.83,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Who has the Rx for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.91,0:21:59.46,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A decriminalized world
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.63,0:22:02.46,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A sanctioned word
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:06.30,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Taking in heat\NJust like "Pirates of Death"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:09.84,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Atone with the game of laws\NBilly in despair
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.93,0:22:12.64,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Now, it's time for ethics\NNow, the unstoppable Eraser Rain
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.47,0:22:15.39,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Billy in despair
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.47,0:22:17.98,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Now, it's time for ethics\NNow, the unstoppable Eraser Rain
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.14,0:22:21.23,Death Note ED2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The unstoppable Eraser Rain
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.08,0:22:38.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki, Watari, Rem...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.50,0:22:41.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All those in my way have disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.67,0:22:46.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the god of the new world.
